30:10.100 --> 30:10.770
- Forum?
- Forum?

30:10.770 --> 30:12.150
- Forum apa?
- Forum apa?

30:12.680 --> 30:14.540
- Cuba tengok.
- Cerminkan skrin.

30:14.640 --> 30:15.640
- Ini dia.
- Mari.

30:16.400 --> 30:18.070
