30:29.260 --> 30:30.140
[seorang jurulatih muda bernama Winfred]

30:32.270 --> 30:34.530
Yongchuan Hengjiu dah ambil orang kita.

30:34.540 --> 30:36.340
Kalau saya jadi kaya suatu hari nanti,

30:36.340 --> 30:38.200
